page.title: 10CLUBS:BROWNIES:FLEET
page.content: THE{BROWNIES PACK}IS CALLED THE{1st {CHICKERELL}.AT{BROWNIES}WE PLAY GAMES LIKE{LADDERS}.WE DO CHALLENGES LIKE MAKING OUR BEDS FOR A WEEK.WE ALSO GO ON OUTINGS.{BROWNIES}MEET ON A{TUESDAY FROM 5:00pm TO 6:30pm.THE{BROWNIES {UNIFORM}IS A{BROWN DRESS}AND A{YELLOW {TIE}WITH A BADGE ON,A{BROWN BELT ,}A HAT,{BROWN SHOES}AND{WHITE SOCKS.}AT{ {BROWNIES}WE CAN EARN BADGES TOO.THE{ {BROWNIES}MUST HAVE SOMETHINGS IN THEIR POCKETS:{A SAFETY PIN, A COMB, A {TISSUE, A PENCIL AND A NOTEBOOK}.THE NAMES OF THE FOUR GROUPS IN THE PACK ARE{'PIXIES', 'ELVES', 'SPRITES'AND {'LEPRECHAUNS'}.OUR ADULT LEADERS ARE CALLED{'BROWN OWL' AND 'TAWNY OWL'.} THEY ARE VERY KIND.THE{BROWNIES}MEET AT THE LOCAL CHURCH.
